# Cursor Execution Harness (Backend)

**Scope:** [`CLAUDE.md`](CLAUDE.md) · **Vault:** `docs/Backend/` only (Frontend vault와 wikilink 분리).

> Root blueprint: repository `CLAUDE.md` (텍스트 경로 — 링크 없음).

---

## Before `backend/` changes

1. Repository root `CLAUDE.md` — blueprint + agent behavior
2. [`CLAUDE.md`](CLAUDE.md) — module pathing, `apps/` siblings, hexagonal layers
3. Same-folder rules: [`db-rules.md`](db-rules.md) · [`entity-rules.md`](entity-rules.md) · [`app-rules.md`](app-rules.md)
4. Domain app: code tree `backend/apps/{app}/_docs/CLAUDE.md`

---

## Quick rules

| Item | Rule |
|------|------|
| `PYTHONPATH` | `apps` — import `titanic.*`, `core.*` (not `backend.apps.*`) |
| Entry | `main.py` — routers + middleware only |
| Run | `start-backend.ps1` → port **8000** |
| Layers | router → `dependencies/*_provider` → interactor → repository |
| `Depends` | Only in providers and routers — **not** inside interactors |
| Secrets | Never commit `backend/.env` |

---

## ML 데이터 척도 (요약)

[`CLAUDE.md`](CLAUDE.md) §8 참고. 피처 전처리 전 반드시 분류:

| 구분 | 척도 | 핵심 |
|------|------|------|
| Categorical | **nominal** | 순서 없음 — 청팀/홍팀/백팀 |
| Categorical | **ordinal** | 순서 있음 — 1.매우낮음 ~ 5.매우높음 |
| Quantitative | **interval** | 원점 없음, 등간격 — 온도, pH, 시간 구간 |
| Quantitative | **ratio** | 원점(0) 있음, 배율 가능 — 나이, 돈, 몸무게 |

---

## Sibling apps

Each peer under `apps/` (`titanic`, `audio`, `user`, …) owns hexagonal tree + optional `_docs/CLAUDE.md`.

