## Self-check

- [ ] Correct app `_docs/` doc read?
- [ ] Logic in the right layer?
- [ ] DB writes have commit/rollback?
- [ ] No secrets in diff?
- [ ] ML 피처 척도(nominal/ordinal/interval/ratio) 분류했는가?
